Data Structures

Here are the data structures with brief descriptions:

fishnet_lsa_functionsThe LSA implementation is current incomplete! Functions, structures, and constants that relate to the built-in implementation of the link state routing algorithm
fishnet_name_functionsFunctions and declarations that interact with the built-in name protocol implementation. Modifing these function pointers allows you to provide your own implementation
